{"tid":958854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜稱將有「九五之尊」柯P：他在練肖話   還是他（韓國瑜）自己？","createTime":"2018-12-28T07:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T08:07:44.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db508dd501a0dc39f979a85d7c234aeda49be1f3","tid":958854,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:07:46.000Z","msg":"韓稱將有「九五之尊」柯：他在練肖話<br />\n<br />\n三立新聞網<br />\n<br />\n記者林恩如／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n行政院昨（27日）上午召開院會，這是六都首長在25日就職後首次的院會。據了解，高雄市長韓國瑜在會中開了一個「九五之尊」的玩笑，逗得在場人士哄堂大笑，但外界也好奇誰是九五之尊？對此，同在場的台北市長柯文哲今受訪被問到此事，他表示，那是韓國瑜在「練肖話」。<br />\n<br />\n昨是行政院第3632次會議，據了解，韓國瑜在會中搞笑地說，「今天是行政院會第3632次會議，3加6等於9，3加2是5，看來在場當中會出現『九五之尊』」，此話一出也逗得賴清德、柯文哲等人笑開懷。至於誰是九五之尊？韓國瑜並未正面回應，僅表示只是開個玩笑緩和氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n而柯文哲今上午主持市府交通會報前，被問到韓國瑜所說的「九五之尊」是指誰？<span style=\"color: red;\">柯文哲表示，「他（韓國瑜）在練肖話（台語）。」媒體接著追問，「還是指你（柯文哲）或是賴清德？」，柯文哲則接話「還是他（韓國瑜）自己？」</span>此話一出，讓媒體記者聽了也哄堂大笑。另外，柯文哲也表示，現在大家都比較忙，他會找時間安排與韓國瑜見面 。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/韓稱將有-九五之尊-柯-他在練肖話-034012284.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%9F%93%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89-%E4%B9%9D%E4%BA%94%E4%B9%8B%E5%B0%8A-%E6%9F%AF-%E4%BB%96%E5%9C%A8%E7%B7%B4%E8%82%96%E8%A9%B1-034012284.html&d=CSuYvDQdr8UAJTJOepUIsP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e18cc0fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/韓稱將有-九五之尊-柯-他在練肖話-034012284.html</a>"},{"pid":"1dd40ddef281ba69573d6d86e0a1df8dd7db97ba","tid":958854,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c240d86623ad2f8c674564f355f6732db0bd8979","tid":958854,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"條友真係on99"},{"pid":"4dabe68087eaf2cf4f93b62f79733d3d9d015650","tid":958854,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"總統跟封建時代帝王係唔同"},{"pid":"70b0969b995bde959aab534c1b6cd29ce4dc5b8a","tid":958854,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓國瑜在會中搞笑地說，「今天是行政院會第3632次會議，3加6等於9，3加2是5，看來在場當中會出現『九五之尊』」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hB6mIBHxYAg/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FhB6mIBHxYAg%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=6d1e937e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb17c5961e039cfa758b6475bab09f722e34813b","tid":958854,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"2+0=2<br />\n1+8=9<br />\n<br />\n2018 = 29<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}